      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" fill="none" viewBox="-2 -2 16 16"><path stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.6" d="M6 2.5v7M2.5 6h7"></path></svg>
      Log Read
